file.name: string_discriminator.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  title: Fruits
  version: "1.0"
paths:
  /:
    get:
      operationId: getRoot
      responses:
        "200":
          description: ""
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/Entity"
components:
  schemas:
    Entity:
      oneOf:
        - $ref: "#/components/schemas/Person"
        - $ref: "#/components/schemas/Organization"
      discriminator:
        propertyName: name
    Person:
      required:
        - name
        - age
      type: object
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
        age:
          type: integer
    Organization:
      required:
        - name
      type: object
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
